  m_Name: dr-sturgeon-day4
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  characterName: Dr. Sturgeon
  characterPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3cadb61783a8ad44abb478954be17e5d, type: 3}
  lines:
  - Those waists don't quit!
  - And neither do you.
  - The Great Dribble has brought me so much.
  - But bringing you is the icing on the cake.
  - The day will come where you will be just a few shmeckles short of making your
    quota.
  - And I will be there to congratulate you.
  - And to show you what these long white fingers are capable of.
  - 'Speaking of shmeckle... '
  - Give us a peak.
  textSpeed: 30
  typingSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: f5d143911732a1f43b570748ed2458a4, type: 3}
